{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-22-1",
 "title": "Setting Course for Griffon Space",
 "summary": "Fed up after days of setting up contacts on Caspar, the disguised intelligence team aboard the Triton -- Bazil McKenzie as Mege Vauki, Kathryn as Mersche, and the Twi'lek Xanatos -- decides to change tack in their hunt for the Death Star. Xanatos reports that courting the CSA looks unpromising and recommends instead approaching the friendly Griffon Alliance through a contact named Evan Decker, who proves to be on leave. The group settles on traveling to Cochran in Griffon territory, with Bazil noting that the recent interrogation of the captured Imperial Moff yielded nothing since Emperor Valak trusts no one. After a routine challenge from the Casperian patrol ship Typhoon, they clear departure and jump away, ultimately being directed onward to the Griffon station Pride 1 to meet a man named Patricio Rey.",
